same as the old boss."

32:21.149 --> 32:26.053
Sheriff, I just wanted to thank you
for your discretion.

32:26.087 --> 32:27.954
These things can always be handled.

32:27.988 --> 32:31.591
"These things"?
So this has happened before?

32:31.625 --> 32:34.760
You know the deal...
tomorrow I'll go visit the girl.

32:34.795 --> 32:37.062
She'll put on a show, but ultimately,

32:37.097 --> 32:39.231
it always comes down to the
number they had in their mind

32:39.265 --> 32:40.866
from the moment they
decided to fuck him.

32:40.900 --> 32:43.001
- Yeah? Dern, right?
- Yeah.

32:43.036 --> 32:46.338
Yeah, you need to go somewhere
I can't see you and stay there.

32:46.372 --> 32:49.006
