32:49.041 --> 32:52.443
- Hood.
- Hey, hey.

33:02.389 --> 33:03.756
5-0, that was not cool.

33:03.790 --> 33:05.858
Benny was just doing his
job, man. What the fuck?

33:05.892 --> 33:09.361
You're under arrest
for rape and aggravated assault.

33:12.199 --> 33:14.801
I'm under arrest?

33:18.238 --> 33:22.942
Okay. Yeah, I'm under arrest.
All right, yeah.

33:22.976 --> 33:24.810
Come and get me.

33:29.750 --> 33:32.018
Sheriff.

33:37.192 --> 33:38.759
Sheriff.

33:44.600 --> 33:47.735
Gotta watch me.

33:47.770 --> 33:51.372
That is cute. I like that.

33:52.607 --> 33:54.708
Looks like you're not
too smart after all.

33:55.710 --> 33:59.346
This what you wanna do?

33:59.381 --> 34:02.216
Ladies and gentlemen, amateur hour.

34:02.284 --> 34:04.853
Let's go.

34:34.884 --> 34:37.119
<i> Come on, Sheriff, let's go.</i>

34:51.502 --> 34:53.603
Get up, bitch!

35:02.346 --> 35:05.315
Get out of my way. Move! Move.

35:05.383 --> 35:07.184
Hood.

35:31.607 --> 35:33.775
