38:24.379 --> 38:26.413
<i>You have the right to remain silent.</i>

38:26.448 --> 38:29.316
<i>Anything you say or do can and
will be held against you in...</i>

38:31.552 --> 38:36.757
<i>Sugar here. Come on.
I got you.</i>

38:36.791 --> 38:42.329
<i>All right.
Let's walk, hmm? All right.</i>

38:42.363 --> 38:43.863
So you're just the kind of guy

38:43.898 --> 38:46.266
who makes friends wherever he goes, huh?

38:46.300 --> 38:48.634
Yeah, it's all right.

38:55.110 --> 38:58.245
- Shit.
- Just open the door.

39:11.325 --> 39:15.696
Whoa. I always wanted
to drive one of these.

39:19.467 --> 39:22.403
You cost me a referee
gig tonight, brother.

39:22.438 --> 39:25.373
And I could have used the scratch.

39:36.921 --> 39:41.759
Ha. All righty.
Here we go.

